---
export const prerender = false;
import '../styles/design-system.css';
---

<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <title>NM Statistics - 메인 대시보드</title>
        <style>
            body { font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; background-color: var(--gray-50); margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
            .hero-container { max-width: 900px; width: 100%; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; }
            h1 { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
            p { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
            .grid-menu { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
            .menu-card { 
                padding: 2rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
                display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; text-align: left;
            }
            .menu-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04); border-color: var(--primary); }
            .menu-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
            .menu-title { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-900); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
            .menu-desc { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.5; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="hero-container">
            <h1>NM Statistics</h1>
            <p>핵의학 의약품 및 진료 통계를 위한 통합 분석 플랫폼</p>
            
            <div class="grid-menu">
                <a href="/master-list" class="menu-card card">
                    <span class="menu-icon">📦</span>
                    <span class="menu-title">품목허가 마스터</span>
                    <span class="menu-desc">식약처에 등록된 모든 방사성의약품의 품목 허가 현황 및 기본 정보 조회</span>
                </a>
                <a href="/performance" class="menu-card card">
                    <span class="menu-icon">📈</span>
                    <span class="menu-title">생산·수입 실적</span>
                    <span class="menu-desc">연도별 시장 규모 및 품목별 실적 통계 분석. 필터 및 정렬 기능 제공</span>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="menu-card card" style="opacity: 0.5; pointer-events: none;">
                    <span class="menu-icon">🏢</span>
                    <span class="menu-title">업체별 통계 (준비 중)</span>
                    <span class="menu-desc">공급 업체별 점유율 및 허가 품목 변동 추이 요약</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
